  "texts": [
    "Personalized learning (PL) encompasses various related terms within academic literature, such as customized learning, individualized learning, competency-based learning, differentiated learning, and adaptive learning.",
    "These terms highlight the importance of tailoring educational experiences to individual learner needs and preferences.",
    "While they share attributes with personalized learning, each term has its own distinct focus and approach.",
    "Drawing on Carceles-Poveda & Giannitsarou (2007), Gervais (2016), Kerr (2016), Morgan (2014), Ness & Middleton (2012), Sharma et al. (2017), and US Department of Education (2017), we provide concise definitions for each term:",
    "• Customized learning: Aligns instruction with specific goals or standards (Sharma et al., 2017)."
  ],
